channel.title: Wont run! not newbie question
channel.description:
alright ive been running my server for a few days now, i compiled a lot the past few days and its ran just fine till 10 minutes ago, i compiled it came up normal- no biggy!
buuttttttttt
the server run.bat decided to impose upon itself that it doesnt want to run, even after a clean compile
it comes up like this..
at java.lang double.parsedouble(double.java:540) at server.world.ItemHandler.loadItemlist(itemhandler.java:328) at server.world.itemhandler.(init)(itemhandler.java:31) at server.server.(clinit)(server.java:61)
and thats it, and so you guys dont tell me too look at itemhandler line 328 or 31, or line 61 for the server file.. i definitely did all that and its all clean. Server 61 loads item.
line 328 item handler.. something about token crap, that i havent messed with.
line 31 loads itemlist item.cfg
and server line 61 loads itemhandler....
also checked line 540, and 1011 in item.cfg.. i didnt mess with those either... helppp
someone help me and point me the right ddirrecttionnnn pleasee!!
